$ Excel Object Model: WorksheetView
@ WorksheetView

The `WorksheetView` object controls «Look and Feel» settings.

{ Display* properties

  The interesting properites start with `Display*`:
  table { ll
    `DisplayFormulas` ☰ display or hide → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas[formulas]
    `DisplayGridlines` ☰ 
    `DisplayHeadings` ☰
    `DisplayOutline` ☰
    `DisplayZeros` ☰
  table }

